{% block tab_content %}
<div class="report">
    <p class="lede">Design tokens store static values for a variety of design attributes. Use them in place of hardcoded values to ensure consistency in your user-interface.</p>

    {{ docs.heading('h2', 'Colour') }}

    <p>See the <a href="colour-and-state">colour and state guide</a> for information on the colour design tokens.</p>

